>PROBLEM
Input Format

A single line containing the thickness value for the logo.

Constraints

The thickness must be an odd number.

Output Format

Output the desired logo.

>SOLUTION

# Enter your code here. Read input from STDIN. Print output to STDOUT

c = "H"

threshold = int(input())

#For cap
for i in range(threshold):
    print((c*i).rjust(threshold-1) + c + (c*i).ljust(threshold-1))
    
    
# For pillars

for i in range(threshold+1):
    print((c*threshold).center(2*threshold) + 
          (c*threshold).center(6*threshold))
          
# For horizontal belt

for i in range((threshold+1)//2):
    print((c*(threshold*5)).center(threshold*6))
    
for i in range(threshold+1):
    print((c*threshold).center(2*threshold) + 
          (c*threshold).center(6*threshold))
          
#for cap

for i in range(threshold):
        print(((c*(threshold-i-1)).rjust(threshold) + c + (c*(threshold-i-1)).ljust(threshold)).rjust(threshold*6))

